fields.name: SS24 TS BUTTERFLY Parakeet
fields.description:
A universal loose-fit T-shirt made from medium-weight cotton fabric and complemented by a convenient chest pocket.
The front and back of the T-shirt are decorated with abstract prints of butterflies and a quote from American writer and scientist Carl Sagan:
"We are like mayflies, fluttering out into the world for a day, thinking that this is eternity."

Material: 100% cotton, density 240g
Medium-weight fabric
Universal loose fit, unisex
Prints are applied using silk-screen printing and printed by the МЕЧ team in Moscow.

fields.name: Rare puffer
fields.description:
High-quality, warm oversized down jacket for the Russian winter.
Guaranteed to last several seasons.

-Membrane and water-repellent fabric.
-Swan down filler.
-Branded fittings.
-YKK and SBS zippers.
Temperature range up to -30°.

fields.name: Pertex Matte Balaclava Puffa
fields.description: The Palace Pertex Matte Balaclava Puffa is a cold-weather outerwear piece with a focus on functionality and quality. Crafted from Pertex Quantum lightweight ripstop fabric, this jacket is durable and light. Inside, it boasts 700 Fill Power 90/10 grey duck down for superior warmth. The included pull-out balaclava, stored in the hood's zip compartment, offers additional protection. Made from a blend of polyester and spandex, the balaclava is stretchy and insulating. The all-black colorway adds versatility to any outfit.
